__ NOV TELEFON

__kopiraj iz NAS v downloads
__Instaliraj termux & termux boot

https://f-droid.org/en/packages/com.termux/
https://f-droid.org/en/packages/com.termux.boot/

__zaženi Termux

__dolgo drži tipko na ekran in MORE in označi KEEP SCREEN ON

__Instaliraj ssh - 6x YES
pkg update -y && pkg upgrade -y && pkg install wget -y && pkg install openssh -y && pkg install net-tools -y && sshd

__Če je error - to nekam vnesi ???:
echo "#sshd: no hostkeys available -- exiting"

ssh-keygen -A && whoami

__Ustvari password b-7
passwd u0_a

ifconfig

ssh u0_a@192.168.100. -p 8022

__install UBUNTU in Termux

pkg update -y && pkg install curl proot tar -y && curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AndronixApp/AndronixOrigin/master/Installer/Ubuntu/ubuntu.sh | bash

__Auto boot ubuntu
nano ~/.termux/termux.properties

__Zbriši # pred:
# allow-external-apps = true

mkdir -p ~/.termux/boot && nano ~/.termux/boot/start.sh

__vsebina (kopiraj pol/pol):

#!/data/data/com.termux/files/usr/bin/sh
termux-wake-lock
sshd
am startservice --user 0 -n com.termux/com.termux.app.RunCommandService \
-a com.termux.RUN_COMMAND \

--es com.termux.RUN_COMMAND_PATH '~/start-ubuntu.sh' \
--es com.termux.RUN_COMMAND_WORKDIR '/data/data/com.termux/files/home' \
--ez com.termux.RUN_COMMAND_BACKGROUND 'false' \
--es com.termux.RUN_COMMAND_SESSION_ACTION '0'

__Naj bo datoteka izvršljiva :
chmod +x ~/.termux/boot/start.sh


_____RESTART PHONE____

zaženi TERMUX in avtomatsko se mora postavitiv UBUNTU (malo počakaj)

__če ne - zagon ubuntu :  
./start-ubuntu.sh

__izhod iz ubuntu :  exit

--->  kopiraš v UBUNTU !!!

__nastavi auto start in barve:
apt install -y nano screen && nano ~/.bashrc

odznači #
force_color_prompy=yes

__na koncu dodaj:

#__________MOJE_________
bash -c "sleep 3 && ./ccminer/start.sh" && screen -r
alias rr='screen -x CCminer'
alias xx='screen -X -S CCminer quit && screen -ls'
alias sl='screen -ls'
alias ss='~/ccminer/start.sh'
alias XX='xx'
alias RR='rr'
alias SL='sl'
alias SS='ss'


___ alias rr='screen -x CCminer' && alias xx='screen -X -S CCminer quit && screen -ls' && alias sl='screen -ls' && alias ss='~/ccminer/start.sh' && alias XX='xx' && alias RR='rr' && alias SL='sl' && alias SS='ss'

__link na github, ostalo se izvede samo

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BLBMS/Android-Mining/main/install.sh && chmod +x install.sh && ./install.sh

__v JSON menjaj ime delavca - se postavi avtomatsko

__pojdi v SETTINGS 
__pod APPS -> Termux označi "Appear on top" !!!!!!!!
__S10 pod "Notification/Advanced Settings" označi "App icon badges" "Battery percentage" !!!
__J7 pod ...  "Custom restr." odznači "Hide notif. dots on app icons"

__potregni dol ekran in vklopi: "Acquire Wakelock"  ->  (wake lock held)

__na "Stop optimizing battery ... "  -> Alow

__zaženi Termux.BOOT

__RESTART PHONE

__zaženeš UBUNTU, če se ni sam ga z:
./start.sh

